      "content": "but people don't understand the weight of this. they talk about \"getting through it\" like it's something you do with effort, but i don't have any strength left. there's a certain grace in just giving in, isn't there? to stop fighting the current and just let the water take you. it feels more honest than pretending i can survive this. it feels like the only way to truly be at peace.",
